plot: In this remake of the 1973 horror hit &"The Exorcist&", a 12 year old girl named Gul, living with her mother in a cozy, high society life in Istambul becomes possessed by the Satan himself through a Ouija board and a troubled psychiatrist and an experienced exorcist become the girl's only hope for salvation.   Written by  matheusmarchetti
